{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6cda0bf0-9310-5418-9c08-3f1a93d3e4bc","html":"<h2 id=\"papers-we-love\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#papers-we-love\" aria-label=\"papers we love permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"http://paperswelove.org/images/logo-top.svg\" alt=\"Papers We Love\"></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://gitter.im/papers-we-love/community?utm_source=badge&#x26;utm_medium=badge&#x26;utm_campaign=pr-badge\"><img src=\"https://badges.gitter.im/papers-we-love/community.svg\" alt=\"Gitter\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>Papers We Love</strong> (<em>PWL</em>) is a community built around reading, discussing and learning more about academic computer science papers. This repository serves as a directory of some of the best papers the community can find, bringing together documents scattered across the web. You can also visit the <a href=\"http://paperswelove.org/\">Papers We Love site</a> for more info.</p>\n<p>Due to <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/blob/master/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md#respect-content-licenses\">licenses</a> we cannot always host the papers themselves (when we do, you will see a <img class=\"emoji-icon\" alt=\"emoji-scroll\" data-icon=\"emoji-scroll\" style=\"display: inline; margin: 0; margin-top: 1px; position: relative; top: 5px; width: 25px\" src=\"data:image/png;base64, \" title=\"emoji-scroll\" /> emoji next to its title in the directory README) but we can provide links to their locations.</p>\n<p>If you enjoy the papers, perhaps stop by a local chapter meetup and join in on the vibrant discussions around them. You can also discuss <em>PWL</em> events, the content in this repository, and/or anything related to <em>PWL</em> on our <a href=\"https://paperswelove.slack.com/messages/general/\">Slack</a>, after <a href=\"http://papersweloveslack.herokuapp.com/\">signing-up</a> to join it, or on our <em>#paperswelove</em> IRC channel on freenode.</p>\n<h3 id=\"chapters\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#chapters\" aria-label=\"chapters permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Chapters</h3>\n<p>Here are our official chapters. Let us know if you are interested in <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/wiki/Creating-a-PWL-chapter\">starting one</a> in your city!</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-amsterdam/\">Amsterdam</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Athens\">Athens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Atlanta\">Atlanta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-we-love-Bangalore/\">Bangalore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-bcn/\">Barcelona</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Belfast/\">Belfast</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Berlin/\">Berlin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/pwlbbsr/\">Bhubaneswar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Boston-Cambridge/\">Boston</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-bsb\">Brasilia</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-bucharest/\">Bucharest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://paperswelove.org/buenos-aires/\">Buenos Aires</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Cairo/\">Cairo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Chattanooga/\">Chattanooga</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-chicago/\">Chicago</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Columbus/\">Columbus, Ohio</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Gothenburg/\">Gothenburg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Hamburg/\">Hamburg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-hyderabad/\">Hyderabad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/techcorridorio\">Iowa City</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/PapersWeLoveKathmandu/\">Kathmandu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/PapersWeLoveKyiv\">Kyiv</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.paperswelovelb.club\">Lebanon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-london\">London</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-la\">Los Angeles</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Madrid/\">Madrid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Montreal/\">Montreal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love/\">New York City</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Paris/\">Paris</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Doo-Things\">Pune</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Raleigh-Durham/\">Raleigh-Durham</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/papers-we-love-rio-de-janeiro/\">Rio de Janeiro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-San-Diego/\">San Diego</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/papers-we-love-too/\">San Francisco</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Seattle/\">Seattle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/seoul-tech-society\">Seoul, Korea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/paperswelovesg/\">Singapore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-in-saint-louis/\">St. Louis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Papers-We-Love-Teresina/\">Teresina</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Toronto/\">Toronto</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-Vienna/\">Vienna</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Papers-We-Love-DC-NoVA/\">Washington, DC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pwlwpg.ca/\">Winnipeg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Papers-we-love-Zurich/\">Zürich</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>All of our meetups follow our <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/blob/master/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md\">Code of Conduct</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"past-presentations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#past-presentations\" aria-label=\"past presentations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Past Presentations</h3>\n<p>Check out our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/PapersWeLove\">YouTube</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mixcloud.com/paperswelove/\">MixCloud</a> (audio-only format) channels.</p>\n<h2 id=\"info\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#info\" aria-label=\"info permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Info</h2>\n<p>We're looking for pull requests related to papers we should add, better organization of the papers we do have, and/or links to other paper-repos we should point to.</p>\n<h3 id=\"other-good-places-to-find-papers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#other-good-places-to-find-papers\" aria-label=\"other good places to find papers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other Good Places to Find Papers</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/keeroyz\">2 Minute Papers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bell-labs.com/our-research/technical-journal/\">Bell System Technical Journal, 1922-1983</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://jeffhuang.com/best_paper_awards.html\">Best Paper Awards in Computer Science</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://research.fb.com/publications/\">Facebook</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://scholar.google.com/citations?view_op=top_venues&#x26;hl=en&#x26;vq=eng\">Google Scholar</a> (choose a subcategory)</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://research.microsoft.com/apps/catalog/default.aspx?t=publications\">Microsoft Research</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://alexott.net/en/fp/books/\">Functional Programming Books Review</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://dspace.mit.edu/handle/1721.1/39813\">MIT's Artificial Intelligence Lab Publications</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://dsrg.pdos.csail.mit.edu/\">MIT's Distributed System's Reading Group</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://arxiv.org/\">arXiv Paper Repository</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://scirate.com/\">SciRate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://doc.cat-v.org/\">cat-v.org</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://yarchive.net/comp/index.html\">y-archive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.netlib.org/\">netlib</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mmcgrana/services-engineering\">Services Engineering Reading List</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mmcgrana/services-engineering\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.2k</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://christophermeiklejohn.com/distributed/systems/2013/07/12/readings-in-distributed-systems.html\">Readings in Distributed Systems</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://samth.github.io/gradual-typing-bib/\">Gradual Typing Bibliography</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.covert.io/the-definitive-security-datascience-and-machinelearning-guide/\">Security Data Science Papers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~rwh/papers/index.html\">Research Papers from Robert Harper, Carnegie Mellon University</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://lobste.rs/t/pdf\">Lobste.rs tagged as PDF</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://blog.acolyer.org/\">The Morning Paper</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please check out our <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/wiki/Other-Good-Sources-of-Reading-Material\">wiki-page</a> for links to blogs, books, exchanges that are worth a good read.</p>\n<h3 id=\"how-to-read-a-paper\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-read-a-paper\" aria-label=\"how to read a paper permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How To Read a Paper</h3>\n<p>Reading a paper is not the same as reading a blogpost or a novel. Here are a few handy resources to help you get started.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://organizationsandmarkets.com/2010/08/31/how-to-read-an-academic-article/\">How to read an academic article</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cc.gatech.edu/~akmassey/posts/2012-02-15-advice-on-reading-academic-papers.html\">Advice on reading academic papers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://violentmetaphors.com/2013/08/25/how-to-read-and-understand-a-scientific-paper-2/\">How to read and understand a scientific paper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://michaelrbernste.in/2014/10/21/should-i-read-papers.html\">Should I Read Papers?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8eRx5Wo3xYA\">The Refreshingly Rewarding Realm of Research Papers</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"applicationsideas-built-around-papers-we-love\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#applicationsideas-built-around-papers-we-love\" aria-label=\"applicationsideas built around papers we love permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Applications/Ideas built around Papers We Love</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Love a Paper - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/loveapaper\">@loveapaper</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"download-papers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#download-papers\" aria-label=\"download papers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Download papers</h3>\n<p>Open your favourite terminal and run:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ ./scripts/download.sh</code></pre></div>\n<p>This will scrape markdown files for links to PDFs and download papers to their respective directories.</p>\n<p>See <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/blob/master/scripts/README.md\">README.md</a> for more options.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contributing-guidelines\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing-guidelines\" aria-label=\"contributing guidelines permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contributing Guidelines</h2>\n<p>Please take a look at our <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/blob/master/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md\">CONTRIBUTING.md</a> file.</p>\n<h2 id=\"copyright\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#copyright\" aria-label=\"copyright permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Copyright</h2>\n<p>The name \"Papers We Love\" and the logos for the organization are copyrighted, and under the ownership of Papers We Love Ltd, all rights reserved. When starting a chapter, please review <a href=\"https://github.com/papers-we-love/papers-we-love/wiki/Creating-a-PWL-chapter\">our guidelines</a> and ask us about using the logo.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#papers-we-love\"><img src=\"http://paperswelove.org/images/logo-top.svg\" alt=\"Papers We Love\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#chapters\">Chapters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#past-presentation